TITLE
    WWW::Shorten::iiipe

DESCRIPTION
    This module provides interface for the URL shortening service
    http://iii.pe

SYNOPSIS
        use WWW::Shorten::iiipe;
        my $short_url = makeashorterlink( $long_url );

SUBROUTINES
  makeashorterlink( $url, %args )
    Takes a required $url and optional arguments and returns a shortened
    url. The single optional argument available is "ttl", specifying the
    shortened link' time-to-live value in seconds. The default is 86400.

SEE ALSO
    WWW::Shorten

    <http:/iii.pe>

